           email = "m.d.manurung@lumc.nl"))
Description: Implements Robust Angle-based Joint and Individual Variation Explained (RAJIVE) for matched multi-view data. Provides robust singular value decomposition, joint and individual component estimation, diagnostic visualization, feature-level jackstraw testing, metadata association, and stability summaries.
